    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Enjoy the tests 1, 4, 7, 11, and 12 that <i>Umbral Alchemy</i> has prepared exclusively for you! Discover the secrets hidden in the weird materials with Bill's guide.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>General description:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In <strong>Unlighted</strong> you will play as a test subject that works for  <i>Umbral Alchemy</i>, a company dedicated to the research of weird stones with mysterious properties never seen before by humans. Thanks to you they hope to discover the origin of these weird materials, but it won't be an easy path.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051540/extras/2340f2c785a2906cfde482b48a056eb4.poster.avif?t=1757349532\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051540/extras/2340f2c785a2906cfde482b48a056eb4.webm?t=1757349532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051540/extras/2340f2c785a2906cfde482b48a056eb4.mp4?t=1757349532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will solve puzzles in first person using a scanner for given by <i>Umbral Alchemy</i>. With a minimalist and oppressive graphic style, accompanied by sounds and music that will create nerves, tension and an eerie feeling through the tests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >                       <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051540/extras/9950f7aafbdc3c61ffff90d0f78695ae.poster.avif?t=1757349532\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051540/extras/9950f7aafbdc3c61ffff90d0f78695ae.webm?t=1757349532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051540/extras/9950f7aafbdc3c61ffff90d0f78695ae.mp4?t=1757349532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Gameplay:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By using the scanner, you will have to observe where the key parts will be to solve the puzzles that <i>Umbral Alchemy</i> will pose. Make the Umbralita appear to succeed on the tests that Bill presents to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051540/extras/580e8d68dd7ec6b058ae170d2a188f79.avif?t=1757349532\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3051540/extras_big/580e8d68dd7ec6b058ae170d2a188f79.avif?t=1757349532 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
